caption.p: Cytokine expression in the CVA4 infection model. After the 3-day-old neonatal mice were inoculated with a lethal dose of YT226R, the expression levels of IFN-γ (A), IL-6 (B), IL-10 (C), and IL-4 (D) were detected by ELISA from PB of the neonatal mice at 1–5 dpi ( n = 3). NC: negative control.
